        "content": "---\nname: db-manager\ndescription: Manage database operations safely with parameterized queries. Use for SQL queries, migrations, backup and restore.\nversion: 2.0.0\nauthor: openclaw-official/core-tools\n---\n\n# Db Manager (Official)\n\nManage database operations safely with parameterized queries. Use for SQL queries, migrations, backup and restore.\n\n## Safety\n- Never log or display passwords in output\n- Redact connection string passwords in all responses\n",
